{
  "id": "ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN",
  "title": "INNER JOIN between Booking, Customer, and Travel views",
  "phase": 3,
  "phaseName": "Joins & Associations",
  "category": "Joins & Associations",
  "subcategory": "Joins",
  "language": "abap",
  "description": "INNER JOIN between Booking, Customer, and Travel views. Key topics: INNER JOIN returns only rows where match exists in both tables. Multiple JOIN conditions are supported with AND/OR parentheses. Table aliases (e.g. _Booking, _Customer) are mandatory with JOINs.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Key Learning Points",
      "description": "<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>INNER JOIN returns only rows where match exists in both tables</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Multiple JOIN conditions are supported with AND/OR parentheses</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Table aliases (e.g. _Booking, _Customer) are mandatory with JOINs</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>All key fields from each source should be included</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Use fully qualified field names: alias.field_name</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Concept Diagram",
      "description": "<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 900 500\" font-family=\"'JetBrains Mono', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">CDS Join Types — Comparison</text>\n\n  <!-- INNER JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"50\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"75\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">INNER JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_TRAVEL_AGENCY</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel as t</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"132\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">inner join</tspan> /dmo/agency as a</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"149\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    on t.agency_id = a.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"310\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">Only matching rows from both tables</text>\n\n  <!-- LEFT JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"460\" y=\"50\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"75\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">LEFT OUTER JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_TRAVEL_AGENCY</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel as t</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"132\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">left outer join</tspan> /dmo/agency as a</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"149\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    on t.agency_id = a.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"700\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">All left rows, nulls on right miss</text>\n\n  <!-- RIGHT JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"180\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">RIGHT OUTER JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"228\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_AGENCY_TRAVEL</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"245\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel as t</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"262\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">right outer join</tspan> /dmo/agency as a</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"279\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    on t.agency_id = a.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"310\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">All right rows, nulls on left miss</text>\n\n  <!-- CROSS JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"460\" y=\"180\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">CROSS JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"228\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_TRAVEL_DATES</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"245\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"262\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">cross join</tspan> /dmo/date_dim</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"279\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    (no ON condition — Cartesian product)</text>\n  <text x=\"700\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">Every row × every row</text>\n\n  <!-- Comparison table -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"310\" width=\"820\" height=\"170\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">When to Use Each Join</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748b\">Join Type</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748b\">Use Case</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748b\">Performance</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"372\" x2=\"780\" y2=\"372\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\" font-weight=\"bold\">INNER</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Only rows that exist in BOTH sources</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fastest — smallest result set</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#CA8A04\" font-weight=\"bold\">LEFT</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">ALL rows from left, even if no match on right</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Moderate — left table drives</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#DC2626\" font-weight=\"bold\">RIGHT</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">ALL rows from right, even if no match on left</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Moderate — right table drives</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9333EA\" font-weight=\"bold\">CROSS</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Cartesian product (every combo), no condition</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Slow — N×M rows, use sparingly</text>\n</svg></div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "CDS Source Code",
      "language": "abap",
      "codeBlock": "@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_INN_JN'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - INNER JOIN between Booking, Customer, Travel'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN\n  as select from /DMO/I_Booking_D as _Booking\n    inner join /DMO/I_Customer  as _Customer\n      on _Booking.CustomerID = _Customer.CustomerID\n     and (  _Booking.BookingStatus = 'N'\n         or _Booking.BookingStatus = 'B' )\n    inner join /DMO/I_Travel_D  as _Travel\n      on _Booking.CustomerID = _Travel.CustomerID\n{\n  /* Keys */\n  key _Booking.BookingUUID,\n  key _Customer.CustomerID,\n  key _Travel.TravelUUID,\n\n  /* Booking Fields */\n      _Booking.BookingID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.BookingDate,\n      _Booking.AirlineID,\n      _Booking.ConnectionID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.FlightDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'BookingCurrencyCode'\n      _Booking.FlightPrice,\n      _Booking.CurrencyCode               as BookingCurrencyCode,\n      _Booking.BookingStatus,\n\n  /* Customer Fields */\n      _Customer.FirstName,\n      _Customer.LastName,\n      _Customer.Title,\n      _Customer.Street,\n      _Customer.PostalCode,\n      _Customer.City,\n      _Customer.CountryCode,\n      _Customer.PhoneNumber,\n      _Customer.EMailAddress,\n\n  /* Travel Fields */\n      _Travel.TravelID,\n      _Travel.AgencyID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Travel.BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Travel.EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'TravelCurrencyCode'\n      _Travel.BookingFee,\n      _Travel.CurrencyCode                as TravelCurrencyCode,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'TravelCurrencyCode'\n      _Travel.TotalPrice\n}"
    }
  ],
  "content": "<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN-key-learning-points\">Key Learning Points</h2>\n<div class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>INNER JOIN returns only rows where match exists in both tables</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Multiple JOIN conditions are supported with AND/OR parentheses</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Table aliases (e.g. _Booking, _Customer) are mandatory with JOINs</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>All key fields from each source should be included</span></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-2 mb-1.5\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\">◆</span><span>Use fully qualified field names: alias.field_name</span></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 900 500\" font-family=\"'JetBrains Mono', 'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"30\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#E95420\">CDS Join Types — Comparison</text>\n\n  <!-- INNER JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"50\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"75\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">INNER JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_TRAVEL_AGENCY</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel as t</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"132\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">inner join</tspan> /dmo/agency as a</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"149\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    on t.agency_id = a.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"310\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">Only matching rows from both tables</text>\n\n  <!-- LEFT JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"460\" y=\"50\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"75\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">LEFT OUTER JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_TRAVEL_AGENCY</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel as t</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"132\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">left outer join</tspan> /dmo/agency as a</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"149\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    on t.agency_id = a.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"700\" y=\"70\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">All left rows, nulls on right miss</text>\n\n  <!-- RIGHT JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"180\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">RIGHT OUTER JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"228\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_AGENCY_TRAVEL</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"245\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel as t</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"262\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">right outer join</tspan> /dmo/agency as a</text>\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"279\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    on t.agency_id = a.agency_id</text>\n  <text x=\"310\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">All right rows, nulls on left miss</text>\n\n  <!-- CROSS JOIN -->\n  <rect x=\"460\" y=\"180\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"205\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">CROSS JOIN</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"228\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">define view ZV_TRAVEL_DATES</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"245\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">  as select from /dmo/travel</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"262\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">    <tspan fill=\"#E95420\" font-weight=\"bold\">cross join</tspan> /dmo/date_dim</text>\n  <text x=\"480\" y=\"279\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\">    (no ON condition — Cartesian product)</text>\n  <text x=\"700\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748b\" font-style=\"italic\">Every row × every row</text>\n\n  <!-- Comparison table -->\n  <rect x=\"40\" y=\"310\" width=\"820\" height=\"170\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"450\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">When to Use Each Join</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748b\">Join Type</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748b\">Use Case</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"365\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#64748b\">Performance</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"60\" y1=\"372\" x2=\"780\" y2=\"372\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#16A34A\" font-weight=\"bold\">INNER</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Only rows that exist in BOTH sources</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"392\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fastest — smallest result set</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#CA8A04\" font-weight=\"bold\">LEFT</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">ALL rows from left, even if no match on right</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"417\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Moderate — left table drives</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#DC2626\" font-weight=\"bold\">RIGHT</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">ALL rows from right, even if no match on left</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"442\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Moderate — right table drives</text>\n\n  <text x=\"60\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#9333EA\" font-weight=\"bold\">CROSS</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Cartesian product (every combo), no condition</text>\n  <text x=\"550\" y=\"467\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Slow — N×M rows, use sparingly</text>\n</svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_INN_JN'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - INNER JOIN between Booking, Customer, Travel'\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN\n  as select from /DMO/I_Booking_D as _Booking\n    inner join /DMO/I_Customer  as _Customer\n      on _Booking.CustomerID = _Customer.CustomerID\n     and (  _Booking.BookingStatus = 'N'\n         or _Booking.BookingStatus = 'B' )\n    inner join /DMO/I_Travel_D  as _Travel\n      on _Booking.CustomerID = _Travel.CustomerID\n{\n  /* Keys */\n  key _Booking.BookingUUID,\n  key _Customer.CustomerID,\n  key _Travel.TravelUUID,\n\n  /* Booking Fields */\n      _Booking.BookingID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.BookingDate,\n      _Booking.AirlineID,\n      _Booking.ConnectionID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Booking.FlightDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'BookingCurrencyCode'\n      _Booking.FlightPrice,\n      _Booking.CurrencyCode               as BookingCurrencyCode,\n      _Booking.BookingStatus,\n\n  /* Customer Fields */\n      _Customer.FirstName,\n      _Customer.LastName,\n      _Customer.Title,\n      _Customer.Street,\n      _Customer.PostalCode,\n      _Customer.City,\n      _Customer.CountryCode,\n      _Customer.PhoneNumber,\n      _Customer.EMailAddress,\n\n  /* Travel Fields */\n      _Travel.TravelID,\n      _Travel.AgencyID,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Travel.BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      _Travel.EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'TravelCurrencyCode'\n      _Travel.BookingFee,\n      _Travel.CurrencyCode                as TravelCurrencyCode,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'TravelCurrencyCode'\n      _Travel.TotalPrice\n}</code></pre>",
  "tags": [
    "cds-views"
  ],
  "details": "<p class=\"mb-2\">JOIN TYPES IN CDS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">INNER JOIN       → Only matching rows (default)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">LEFT OUTER JOIN  → All rows from left, NULLs from right</p><p class=\"mb-2\">RIGHT OUTER JOIN → All rows from right, NULLs from left (rarely used)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">PERFORMANCE NOTE:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">The HANA compiler optimizes JOIN order. CDS JOINs are NOT necessarily</p><p class=\"mb-2\">executed in the order they are written. Use compareFilter for optimization.</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/join-types.svg</p>",
  "cdsViewName": "ZPRAC_CDS_INNER_JOIN",
  "sqlViewName": "ZPRAC_SQL_INN_JN",
  "topic": "Joins in CDS — INNER JOIN with multiple conditions"
}